    • 构造器详细资料

      • LazyParameterizedType

        protected LazyParameterizedType(TypePool typePool,
                                TypeVariableSource typeVariableSource,
                                String typePath,
                                Map<String,List<TypePool.Default.LazyTypeDescription.AnnotationToken>> annotationTokens,
                                String name,
                                List<TypePool.Default.LazyTypeDescription.GenericTypeToken> parameterTypeTokens)
        Creates a new description of a parameterized type.
        参数:
        typePool - The type pool that is used for locating a generic type.
        typeVariableSource - The type variable source to use for resolving type variables.
        typePath - This type's type path.
        annotationTokens - A mapping of the represent type's annotation tokens,
        name - The binary name of the raw type.
        parameterTypeTokens - A list of type tokens representing this type's bounds.

    • 方法详细资料

      • asErasure

        public TypeDescription asErasure()
        从接口复制的说明: TypeDefinition
        Returns the erasure of this type. Wildcard types (TypeDescription.Generic.Sort#WILDCARD) do not have a well-defined erasure and cause an IllegalStateException to be thrown.
        返回:
        The erasure of this type.

      • getTypeArguments

        public TypeList.Generic getTypeArguments()
        从接口复制的说明: TypeDescription.Generic

        Returns the type arguments of this type.

        Parameters are only well-defined for parameterized types (Sort#PARAMETERIZED). For all other types, this method throws an IllegalStateException.

        返回:
        A list of this type's type parameters.

      • getOwnerType

        public TypeDescription.Generic getOwnerType()
        从接口复制的说明: TypeDescription.Generic

        Returns the owner type of this type. A type's owner type describes a nested type's declaring type. If it exists, the returned type can be a non-generic or parameterized type. If a class has no declaring type, null is returned.

        An owner type is only well-defined for parameterized types (Sort#PARAMETERIZED), for non-generic types (Sort#NON_GENERIC) and for generic arrays (Sort#GENERIC_ARRAY). For all other types, this method throws an IllegalStateException.

        返回:
        This type's owner type or null if no owner type exists.

      • getDeclaredAnnotations

        public AnnotationList getDeclaredAnnotations()
        从接口复制的说明: AnnotationSource
        Returns a list of annotations that are declared by this instance.
        返回:
        A list of declared annotations.
